4
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:46,838
I wish you’d stayed to complete your degree.

5
00:00:46,964 --> 00:00:49,716
I know, but I don’t have the money.

6
00:00:49,841 --> 00:00:52,719
Just don’t give up your writing.

7
